{"tid":1745743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府話有事故會收票箱，12月1日先點票！","createTime":"2019-11-22T11:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T14:16:41.000Z","uid":185781,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"563c749b0ee4044641998da7e3e20003add99595","tid":1745743,"uid":185781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNLGUOg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNLGUOg.jpg&h=7883aa97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KS4wxzX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKS4wxzX.jpg&h=29990d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8OmamD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8OmamD.jpg&h=658f1eff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75729e16a1e755f98e0de1b3528eade040c433a1","tid":1745743,"uid":185781,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"政府點解要<br />\nSet &gt;1.5小時事故就要1/12先點票<br />\n就係因為原本政府既三個鐘事故取消選舉策略<br />\n比大家既 730準時投票策略破左功<br />\n<br />\n你諗下 如果730大部份黃既投哂票<br />\n個幾個票箱放係個好*安全*既地方=成箱黃票比佢做手腳換哂做藍票<br />\n到其他投唔到既人（大部份藍絲/老人院一車車票）之後再投<br />\n再加埋呢幾箱原本黃既票（唔好講話黃變藍 就咁成箱唔見哂都仆得街輸硬比建制派啦）"},{"pid":"21ed237e915eba312825ef42dde53855b8330d41","tid":1745743,"uid":185781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:15:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2f2910e231a38b0b086bbbc621d296e0719eea97","tid":1745743,"uid":30966,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:15:58.000Z","msg":"斜恩"},{"pid":"d84dfcb8a57a1a4875720d2f7633bad6630c3e9d","tid":1745743,"uid":185781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:16:37.000Z","msg":"上個post解釋得唔清楚，重新出post"},{"pid":"5b9688059842a21c08562ec4adf0bb034857b08f","tid":1745743,"uid":185781,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"之前有選管會兩部電腦事件<br />\n今次肯撚定會出事<br />\n<